    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Flesh Psychosis</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flesh Psychosis 是一款轻松的益智游戏，您需要将相同的食材配对以烹饪……特别的菜肴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组装食材以将其添加到您的库存中！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每 20 次操作，进入新的烹饪阶段，看看您是否是一个邪恶的好厨师。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帮助 Madline 发现更多可怕的食谱</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同时实现最佳分数 ！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084720/extras/c2486c01faf6ed03766e36ba0328b721.poster.avif?t=1753367661\" width=788 height=434 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084720/extras/c2486c01faf6ed03766e36ba0328b721.webm?t=1753367661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084720/extras/c2486c01faf6ed03766e36ba0328b721.mp4?t=1753367661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以在每回合使用不同的动作，或者掉落新的被诅咒的食物来与其他食物结合并将它们添加到你的库存中。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但要小心——如果他们掉进漏斗里，他们就会迷路！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >为你邪恶的厨房创造可怕的食谱。 </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你可以每回合执行不同的实用操作，或者掉落新的被诅咒的食物，将它们与其他食物结合起来，然后将它们添加到你的库存中。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但要小心，如果他们掉进洞里，他们就会迷路！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在您的邪恶厨房中制作可怕的食谱！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084720/extras/e5af96b6d0e53ae90b9244474750ae53.poster.avif?t=1753367661\" width=788 height=434 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084720/extras/e5af96b6d0e53ae90b9244474750ae53.webm?t=1753367661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084720/extras/e5af96b6d0e53ae90b9244474750ae53.mp4?t=1753367661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏中：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18 个关卡</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10-15 种不同的食材</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10+ 种不同的菜肴。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+ Steam 成就</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无限模式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2-5 小时以上的游戏时间</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持游戏手柄</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小型休闲游戏</p></li></ul>",
